=== facebook_history_names_timeline.pdf ===
Page 1
Facebook History
A concise historical overview with company-name references by day, month, and year where publicly
documented
This report summarizes Facebook''s evolution from a Harvard dorm-room project into the company now known
as Meta Platforms, Inc. Because the brand and the corporate entity have used different names over time, the
timeline below distinguishes the service name "Facebook" from the legal corporate names that operated it.
Important distinction: the social network is still called Facebook. The parent company changed its corporate
name from Facebook, Inc. to Meta Platforms, Inc. in October 2021.[1][4]
